# Vim


## Diff open windows
- do `:diffthis` in each window
- `:diffoff!` stop diff
- `:windo diffthis` to diff all visible windows

## Open file from different branch
:Gedit master:filename

## Sessions
:mks # in current Vim
vim -S Session.vim  # in new Vim

## Profiling
:profile start profile.log
:profile func *
:profile file *
:profile stop

## Run command, sending the buffer as input:
:%! base64
